</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_146" id="73r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ulm </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat unser lieber
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesell Peter Volkmeir, als der
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> von Costencz gen Ulm
                                <expan>kume<ex>n,</ex></expan>
<add>fürbaht</add>, wie er <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>meister</expan>
<expan>fleissiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gebeten hab von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen, ob <add>ir</add>
<add>noch <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> hincziehen icht</add> erfürt von
                        den leuffen und <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czu Costencz, daz ir uns das
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und czu wissen tun wöllet, so
                        ir schierst <add>mügt</add>. Also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                        das also durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen tun wöllet,
                                <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit das füglich sey, als wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersame<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>freunts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> des wol
                            <expan>getr<ex>awen</ex></expan>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        ümb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>sölch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> merern <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen.</expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan> die pasce a xv<hi rend="sup">to</hi>. </ab>
</div>
